35
00:03:34.380 --> 00:03:37.040
- Where the hell are you?
- I'm sorry. I passed out.

36
00:03:37.110 --> 00:03:40.310
I was watching TV.
- That was a premeditated nap.

37
00:03:40.380 --> 00:03:42.370
You did this to me on purpose.

38
00:03:42.450 --> 00:03:44.610
You're my best friend
in the whole universe.

39
00:03:44.690 --> 00:03:46.750
How could you possibly think
a thing like this?

40
00:03:46.820 --> 00:03:49.020
