Thank you!

41
00:03:49.090 --> 00:03:50.490
Forget it. okay?

42
00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:53.080
I didn't want to tell you.
but our little night out has grown.

43
00:03:53.160 --> 00:03:55.490
Huey and I are here
with a few of your closest friends

44
00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:57.550
waiting to wish you a...

45
00:03:58.900 --> 00:04:00.200
Happy birthday?

46
00:04:00.270 --> 00:04:01.360
Happy birthday.

47
00:04:06.440 --> 00:04:08.430
I tried calling you from home.

48
00:04:08.510 --> 00:04:10.700
The girly to end all girlies
is in the house.

49
00:04:10.780 --> 00:04:12.180
Happy birthday. Molly.

50
00:04:12.980 --> 00:04:14.920
We got you. Molly!
- We got you. didn't we?

51
00:04:14.980 --> 00:04:17.980
You did. I thought it was
gonna be just us guys going out.

52
00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:20.650
